  "translations": {
    "en": "The right of your creed's people is harbouring safety, compassion, kindness to their evildoers, drawing them close, reform, thanking their good-doers, keeping harm away. Love for them what you love for yourself. Their elders are like your father, youths like brothers, old women like your mother, children like your own. The right of the protected people is accepting from them what Allah accepted, and not wronging them while they fulfil Allah's covenant. There is no strength save in Allah.",
